EXCEPTION==> An exception is Unexpected/unwanted/abnormal situation that occured at runtime called exception.


Exeption Handling==> in  exception handling we  should have an alternae source through which we  can  handle the exception


* to object orientation mechanism has provided the following techniques to work with.

1. try  2. catch 3.throw 4. throws 5.Finally






class NPE{
public static void main(String[] args){

String str="nitish";
//string str=null;          yha pr ye null ko conversion nhi ho pata to catch() block chalega.
try{
	System.out.println(str.toUpperCase());
}
catch(NullPointerException n)
{
	System.out.println("null cant't be casted");
}
}
}
